<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.201916>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 10. Mitjaevia protuberanta n. sp. 1. Head and thorax, dorsal view. 2. Forewing. 3. Abdominal apodemes. 4. Pygofer lobe, lateral view. 5. Subgenital plate. 6. Style, ventral view. 7. Style, lateral; view. 8. Aedeagus, lateral view. 9. Aedeagus, ventral view. 10. Connective." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/201916/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.201917>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 19. Mitjaevia wangwushana n. sp. 11. Head and thorax, dorsal view. 12. Forewing. 13. Abdominal apodemes. 14. Pygofer lobe, lateral view. 15. Subgenital plate. 16. Style. 17. Aedeagus, lateral view. 18. Aedeagus, ventral view. 19. Connective." ;
